Thought bubbles for special words
<style>
.popup {
  display: inline-block;
  position: relative;
  cursor: pointer;
  color: #ff69b4; /* pink clickable word */
  font-weight: bold;
}

.popup .bubble {
  display: none;
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 120%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  padding: 10px;
  background: #fff;
  border: 2px solid #ff69b4;
